  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The day has finally arrived, today you will become a monster tamer! Make friends with all of them and share a wonderful adventure, together you will explore different areas, take care of the crops and defeat great enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel through several areas to set up camp.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 Powerful bosses.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make friends with over 150 different monsters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 600 different items.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plant and protect crops from wild monsters that will try to eat them.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase the friendship of your monsters.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place various furniture in your base with different uses.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect resources and use them to create different items, potions, weapons and armor.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The day has finally arrived, today you will become a monster tamer! Make friends with all of them and share a wonderful adventure, together you will explore different areas, take care of the crops and defeat great enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel through several areas to set up camp.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 Powerful bosses.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make friends with over 150 different monsters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 600 different items.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plant and protect crops from wild monsters that will try to eat them.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase the friendship of your monsters.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place various furniture in your base with different uses.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect resources and use them to create different items, potions, weapons and armor.</p></li></ul>",
